#: ../../admin-manual/security/csp-headers.rst:80
msgid ""
"**Content-Security-Policy**: This setting will enforce the defined policy. "
"When set, the browser will block any resources (scripts, images, "
"stylesheets, etc.) that violate the policy directives."
msgstr ""
