"developers to test and monitor potential violations without affecting the "
"functionality of the web page. This is useful for testing a new policy or "
"changes to an existing policy without risking breakage. Violations will be "
"reported to the browser's console. This setting is the default."
msgstr ""
"**コンテント・セキュリティ・ポリシー・レポート・オンリー**: このヘッダーは``Content-Security-"
